author: antelder
msg: Enance the apache soap provider to work through a proxy server.
SOAP by default doesn't  take account of the Java system property proxy settings. This change will set the SOAP proxy to be based on the Java system property settings.

author: antelder
msg: Add a new WSIFUtils method (and testcase) to compare strings allowing for a wildcard.
This will be used when adding proxy support to the apache soap provider for the http.nonProxyHosts system property.
